name: rRNA (uridine-N3-)-methyltransferase activity
description: "Catalysis of the reaction: S-adenosyl-L-methionine + rRNA = S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + rRNA containing N3-methyluridine." [GOC:imk, GOC:mah]

name: rRNA (uridine) methyltransferase activity
description: "Catalysis of the reaction: S-adenosyl-L-methionine + rRNA = S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + rRNA containing methyluridine." [GOC:go-curators]

name: cytosolic small ribosomal subunit
description: "The small subunit of a ribosome located in the cytosol." [GOC:mtg_sensu]
